<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.10">
<l>mīṉō ṭāmai kēḻalari kuṟaḷāy muṉṉu mirāmaṉāyt</l>
<l>tāṉāy piṉṉu mirāmaṉāyt tāmō taraṉāyk kaṟkiyum</l>
<l>āṉāṉ ṟaṉṉai kaṇṇapurat taṭiyaṉ kaliya ṉoliceyta</l>
<l>tēṉā riṉcol tamiḻmālai ceppap pāvam nillāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [one] says this Tamil garland of sweet honey-filled speech</l>
<l>Created with the words of the devotee, Kaliyaṉ, on Kaṇṇapuram</l>
<l>About the one who became a fish, turtle, boar, and lion, becoming a dwarf,</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming the prior Rāma,</l>
<l>As himself, as the later Rāma,  as Dāmodara, and Kalki,</l>
<l rend="indent">sins will not persist.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
